data.description: This is an excellent opportunity to enjoy one level living and have rental income to help pay your mortgage! As you enter the left, larger side unit, you immediately step into an inviting open concept kitchen, dining and living room area combination with impressive vaulted ceilings and engineered flooring. The kitchen offers beautiful wood cabinets with sleek granite counter tops. The over-sized main bedroom offers it's own private bathroom suite, while there are two other nicely sized bedrooms; who share their own full bathroom, on the other side of the home. Chill in the air? No problem, walk down the hall into your cozy family room complete with wood-burning stone fireplace and curl up while enjoying the ambiance of the fire. There is also a full unfinished basement with walkout that offerings tons of potential. So bring your imagination!. The adorable smaller right side rental offers two bedrooms and one nicely updated full bathroom.  There is also an updated, eat-in kitchen and nice size living room. Both units have their own washer and dryer hookups. Sitting on a large, level piece of property, this home features an extremely private backyard with partial fencing for separate enjoyment. There are also separate electric meters and hot water heaters, but it does share a single furnace. Located in the Minisink school district this home is an easy commute to schools, highways and shopping! This is definitely a DON'T MISS!
